336
00:22:06,210 --> 00:22:07,910
Zodpoviem sa za to. Neboj sa.

337
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:12,710
Prosím?

338
00:22:13,250 --> 00:22:14,780
Detektív Park. Dobrý deň.

339
00:22:17,250 --> 00:22:18,510
Oh Yeon Joo je zatknutá?

340
00:22:19,210 --> 00:22:20,210
Kde?

341
00:22:21,810 --> 00:22:24,550
- Bola v hoteli.
<i>- Vysielame najnovšie správy.</i>

342
00:22:24,980 --> 00:22:27,809
<i>Totožnosť jediného svedka...</i>

343
00:22:27,810 --> 00:22:30,209
<i>napadnutia riaditeľa IN Global,
Kang Chula,</i>

344
00:22:30,210 --> 00:22:31,410
