Ešte sa nevrátil.

693
00:46:04,450 --> 00:46:08,010
Pravdepodobne je niekde opitý.

694
00:46:08,610 --> 00:46:10,180
Videl som to mnohokrát.

695
00:46:13,380 --> 00:46:14,450
Yeon Joo.

696
00:46:15,480 --> 00:46:16,480
Ukončime to.

697
00:46:17,410 --> 00:46:19,080
